replies.body:
Earlier today we became aware that our players were in fact having disconnection issues. We have a post where you stay up to date on how we are resolving this issue, which you can find [**here**](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/3Lmbjp8Y-3132017-na-server-issues)

We are working on the issue, and appreciate everyone's patience as we get things sorted out.
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
